query:
select 
            sa.id,
            sa.date_epoch_seconds,
            sa.duration_hours,
            sat.type as activity_type,
            sa.description,
            sa.score
            from snowboard_activities as sa
            join snowboard_activity_types as sat on sat.id = sa.type
            where date_epoch_seconds >= ?
            order by date_epoch_seconds asc
